title: Match of the Day 2 - 1st February 2015 - hdtv x264
description:
SPORT: Match of the Day 2
On: BBC 1 HD     
Date: Sunday 1st February 2015 
Time: 22:30 to 23:30 

Mark Chapman presents highlights of the day's two Premier League matches, starting with Arsenal against Aston Villa. Villa have often frustrated the Gunners at the Emirates Stadium, winning on three of their last six league visits, including a 3-1 victory on the opening day of the 2013-14 season. In the second game, Southampton play host to Swansea, a fixture the Saints have historically enjoyed in the recent past. The south coast club are unbeaten in their five previous Premier League meetings, winning each of the last three. The studio experts are Martin Keown and Kevin Kilbane.
